      "id": 24,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "orphan_kill: orphaned dialogs vs un-reaped residual",
      "description": "Per orphan_kill event: dialogs orphaned by the abrupt UAC kill vs the residual still un-reaped after the wait window. Residual\u22480 = reaper healthy.",
