    {
      "id": 34,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Ghost gap = b2bua_active \u2212 sipp_current (double-serve leak detector, ADR-0014)",
      "description": "The robust HA leak signal: a healthy cluster keeps b2bua_active \u2248 sipp_current (gap ~0 + scrape skew). A gap that RISES and STAYS risen after a worker reboot = a double-served takeover copy the reclaimed primary now also serves (self-release failed) or an eager-takeover storm \u2014 the exact regression ADR-0014 (commit 12ae92f) must not reintroduce. Threshold line = REBOOT_GHOST_TOL (300).",
